## Project context
- Frontend stack: vanilla JavaScript, HTML, CSS
- Main files: `index.html`, `styles.css`, `app.js`
- Data is loaded from local JSON files in `data/`
- The site is a static frontend served locally
- No frontend framework is used
- JSON is typically loaded with `fetch(...)`
- UI is rendered client-side in `app.js`

---

## Requirements
- Add the minimum code needed to implement the feature
- Reuse existing structure and styling patterns where possible
- Do not introduce frameworks or unnecessary abstractions
- Keep the implementation easy to understand and edit manually
- Prefer small, targeted changes over broad rewrites

